<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> Before 1 July 1997, and every two years thereafter, the Commission shall examine the implementation of this Directive and the development of the market for digital television services throughout the European Union and submit a report to the European Parliament, to the Council and to the Economic and Social Committee. </inglise>
